Pre-Game Insights: Pakistan and New Zealand are preparing for a five-match T20I series with Babar Azam leading Pakistan and Michael Bracewell captaining New Zealand.
The series marks the return of Mohammad Amir and Imad Wasim to international cricket after their retirements.
Miscellaneous Highlights: This is New Zealand's third visit to Pakistan within 17 months, following previous series in December 2022-January 2023 and April 2023.
Others: The article provides live streaming and broadcast details for the series, including platforms like A Sports HD, Sling TV, and others.
